OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FThe number of people recruited into
OL,8,Fthe Welsh NHS as physician associates
OL,9,Fin secondary care has increased by
OL,10,Fmore than 200% in three years, an
OL,11,Finvestigation by ITV Cymru Wales has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,15,FCymru, which represents thousands of
OL,16,Fdoctors in Wales, says its members are
OL,17,Falready reporting incidents where they
OL,18,Fsay they witnessed the safety of
OL,19,Fpatients being put at risk.
