OL,3,CTripling of physician associates
OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FUsing Freedom of Information (FOI)
OL,8,Flaws, ITV Cymru Wales has found that
OL,9,F105 physician associates have been
OL,10,Frecruited into secondary care in
OL,11,Fhealth boards across Wales.
OL,13,FThe total number of people working in
OL,14,Fthe role now stands at 156. That
OL,15,Frepresents an increase of at least
OL,16,F207%. We cannot be certain that is an
OL,17,Fexact figure because we do not know
OL,18,Fhow many PAs have left the Welsh NHS
OL,19,Fin that time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/21
