OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FThe FOI responses show that 67% of all
OL,8,Fthe physician associates employed in
OL,9,Fsecondary care in Wales have been
OL,10,Femployed in just the last 3 years.
OL,12,FBecoming a physician associate
OL,13,Frequires a two year course on top of a
OL,14,Fdegree qualification.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/21
