OL,3,CTripling of physician associates
OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FThe Chair of the BMA's Welsh Council,
OL,8,FDr Iona Collins, told ITV Cymru Wales:
OL,9,F"The problem is if you have people who
OL,10,Fhave graduated from a variety of other
OL,11,Fdegrees who are under the impression
OL,12,Fthat they are being fast-tracked to
OL,13,Fbecome associated with doctors.
OL,15,F"And instead of training to become
OL,16,Fdoctors, they can train to be like
OL,17,Fdoctors. The two year course is really
OL,18,Fintensive and it facilitates them to
OL,19,Ffeel like a doctor, but not a doctor,
OL,20,Fso they are associated with doctors.
OL,21,FThat is the problem.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
