OL,7,FWhilst these roles can work
OL,8,Fautonomously, they must always work
OL,9,Funder the supervision of a named,
OL,10,Ffully trained and experienced doctor."
OL,12,FThe Welsh Conservatives health
OL,13,Fspokesperson in the Senedd, Sam
OL,14,FRowlands MS said the increase in the
OL,15,Fnumber of physician associates is
OL,16,F"really significant".
