OL,7,F"It perhaps points to a direction of
OL,8,Ftravel which for many people may be a
OL,9,Fconcerned. When people go to hospital
OL,10,Fthey expect to see a doctor, not
OL,11,Fperhaps someone with a lesser
OL,12,Fqualification.
OL,14,F"That's not to underplay the role of
OL,15,Fphysician associates, who play an
OL,16,Fimportant role but that needs to be
OL,17,Fput in the right context."
