OL,7,FMabon ap Gwynfor MS, Plaid Cymru said:
OL,8,F"There's a role for physician
OL,9,Fassociates, absolutely. But that's not
OL,10,Fat the expense of GPs and doctors.
OL,12,F"So, we need to see the government
OL,13,Fensure that they have a programme to
OL,14,Frecruit more GPs in Wales and to
OL,15,Fretain the GPs that we have got."
