OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FMaxine Hanson-Nortey is one of the
OL,8,Fphysician associates recruited in the
OL,9,Flast three years in Wales. She works
OL,10,Fin acute care in Withybush Hospital in
OL,11,FHaverfordwest and is very passionate
OL,12,Fabout her role.
OL,14,F"My role as a physician associate is
OL,15,Factually working alongside doctors,
OL,16,Fsupporting them with decision making,
OL,17,Fdiagnosing patients and managing
OL,18,Fpatients".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/21
