OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FBut Maxine accepts that members of the
OL,8,Fpublic often do not understand the
OL,9,Flimitations of her role in secondary
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,F"You always have to explain to them
OL,13,Fthat this is what I do and my role is
OL,14,Fthis. Some of them don't get it. They
OL,15,Fkeep on describing us as doctors, but
OL,16,Fwe just have to be stressing that
OL,17,Fwe're not doctors".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/21
