OL,7,FMaxine says she doesn't listen to the
OL,8,Fgeneral criticism about the role of
OL,9,Fphysician assistants being
OL,10,Fincreasingly used in Welsh healthcare
OL,11,Fsettings.
OL,13,F"I'm not trying to put my head under
OL,14,Fthe sand, but I don't follow it,
OL,15,Fbecause following is going to bring
OL,16,Fyou down. I've done the course. I've
OL,17,Fbeen trained.
OL,19,F"I treat every patient as they're my
OL,20,Frelative, and I know my limits. I'm
OL,21,Fnot a doctor".
