OL,7,FThe Welsh Conservatives says clarity
OL,8,Faround the role is important and they
OL,9,Fwould support a conversation about
OL,10,Frenaming the role as physician
OL,11,Fassistants, rather than associates,
OL,12,Fwhich is a call from the BMA.
