OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,F"Sadly", Dr Collins says, "we have the
OL,8,Fsituation where people believe they
OL,9,Fhave been training to a level they
OL,10,Fhave not been trained to attain, and
OL,11,Fthey believe they are safe enough to
OL,12,Fdeliver a certain type of care that
OL,13,Fdoctors who have been trained to
OL,14,Fdeliver that care are quite concerned
OL,15,Fand frightened".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/21
