OL,7,FDr Collins says she has been told
OL,8,Fabout incidents where patients have
OL,9,Fexperienced a delay to seeing the
OL,10,Fcorrect level of medical professional
OL,11,Fwhen a physician associate was
OL,12,Fmistaken for a doctor by hospital
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,FShe says doctors have reported to her
OL,16,Foccasions where a patient believed
OL,17,Fthey have had treatment from a doctor
OL,18,Fand then retrospectively found out it
OL,19,Fwas in fact a physician ssociate, and
OL,20,Fthat had led to the wrong clinical
OL,21,Fmanagement.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/21
