OL,4,Cleaves doctors 'concerned and
OL,5,Cfrightened'
OL,7,FDoctors have already reported to the
OL,8,FBMA in Wales about occasions when PAs
OL,9,Fhave proscribed medication and ordered
OL,10,FX-Rays without doctor approval, which
OL,11,Fwould be illegal.
OL,13,F"I want to emphasise that this is not
OL,14,Fabout people", Dr Collins told me,
OL,15,F"This is about the role.
OL,17,FDo you feel like a major incident is
OL,18,Faround the corner, with regards to
OL,19,Fthis blurred line between what is a
OL,20,Fdoctor and what is a physician?", I
OL,21,Fasked her.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/21
