OL,7,F"It is, I'm sorry to say that these
OL,8,Fincidents are already happening in
OL,9,FWales".
OL,11,FFrom December this year, the General
OL,12,FMedical Council (GMC) is set to begin
OL,13,Fregulating Physician Associates and
OL,14,FAnaesthesia associates. The BMA says
OL,15,Fthis will reinforce confusion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/21
