OL,7,FIt believes the Health and Care
OL,8,FProfessions Council, who regulate
OL,9,Fother health professions such as
OL,10,Fphysiotherapists, paramedics and
OL,11,Fradiographers, would be a more
OL,12,Fappropriate regulatory body for PAs,
OL,13,Fgiven the GMC has previously only
OL,14,Fregulated medical practitioners like
OL,15,Fdoctors only.
