OL,7,FA survey last year carried out by the
OL,8,FBMA, which had more than 900
OL,9,Frespondents in Wales, found that 83%
OL,10,Fof doctors who gave their opinion do
OL,11,Fnot understand the difference between
OL,12,Fa doctor and a medical associate
OL,13,Fprofessional.
OL,15,FWhen asked if the way MAPs work within
OL,16,Fthe Welsh NHS poses a risk to patient
OL,17,Fsafety, 25.1% responded always, with
OL,18,F55.3% responding sometimes.
