OL,7,FThe Welsh Government says a tripartite
OL,8,Fgroup has recently been established by
OL,9,FNHS Wales Employers, including BMA,
OL,10,FHealth Education and Improvement Wales
OL,11,Fand Welsh Government.
OL,13,FThis group is tasked with developing a
OL,14,Fframework for the safe and effective
OL,15,Fdeployment of physician associates in
OL,16,FWales.
